                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Sketch point <m>I'</m>, the image of <m>I</m> under the transformation that takes
                    <m>ABCD</m> to <m>A'B'C'D'</m>. How is the location of <m>I'</m> related 
