                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    Sketch point <m>J'</m> the image of <m>J</m> under the transformation that takes
                    <m>ABCD</m> to <m>A'B'C'D'</m>. How is the location of <m>J'</m> related 
                    to <m>A'B'C'D'</m>?
                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
    </task>
    <task>
        <statement>
            <p>
                Based on the translation you explored in 
                <xref ref="app-translate-wcoords"/>, describe in your own words 
